Class EmptyTile

java.lang.Object
java.util.Observable
model.Tile
model.EmptyTile
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class EmptyTile extends Tile
Represents an empty, non-solid tile in the game world. Entities can pass through it without collision.
